{"inkVersion":20,"root":[["ev","str","^Tempy","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"speaker_name","re":true},"^So, uh... that level was pretty bad.","\n","ev","str","^Gus","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"speaker_name","re":true},"ev","str","^right","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"active_sprite","re":true},"ev","str","^Sad","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"right_sprite","re":true},"^Okay, I kinda saw this one coming.","\n","ev","str","^Tempy","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"speaker_name","re":true},"ev","str","^left","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"active_sprite","re":true},"ev","str","^Sad","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"left_sprite","re":true},"^I know the time limit is something only I have to deal with, and it won't affect regular players...","\n","ev","str","^Annoyed","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"left_sprite","re":true},"^..but even ignoring that, this level was way too boring. All I did was wait for platforms to move me around to where I needed to be.","\n","^Why did you make them go that slow?","\n","ev","str","^Gus","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"speaker_name","re":true},"ev","str","^right","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"active_sprite","re":true},"ev","str","^Despairing","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"right_sprite","re":true},"^I know, I know! I'm sorry!","\n","ev","str","^Gus","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"speaker_name","re":true},"ev","str","^right","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"active_sprite","re":true},"ev","str","^Sad","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"right_sprite","re":true},"^I wanted the platforms to move faster! And the level to be cooler and harder! But!","\n","^It turned out that it was way too hard to land on the platforms when they were moving quickly.","\n","ev","str","^Tempy","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"speaker_name","re":true},"ev","str","^left","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"active_sprite","re":true},"ev","str","^Default","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"left_sprite","re":true},"^Oh.","\n","ev","str","^Gus","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"speaker_name","re":true},"ev","str","^right","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"active_sprite","re":true},"ev","str","^Sad","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"right_sprite","re":true},"^I ended up slapping together an easier level with slow platforms instead.","\n","ev","str","^Tempy","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"speaker_name","re":true},"ev","str","^left","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"active_sprite","re":true},"ev","str","^Default","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"left_sprite","re":true},"^Well, that makes some sense, but that doesn't make the level suddenly good.","\n","^And we probably can't keep using moving platforms at this speed throughout the game, or they're going to be really boring.","\n","ev","str","^Despairing","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"left_sprite","re":true},"^(Also I don't think I'd be able to keep finishing levels in time if I keep using these)","\n","ev","str","^Gus","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"speaker_name","re":true},"ev","str","^right","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"active_sprite","re":true},"ev","str","^Sad","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"right_sprite","re":true},"^Yeah, you're probably right. What could we do to fix it though?","\n","ev","str","^Confused","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"right_sprite","re":true},"^Hm... I guess I can just make the platforms bigger?","\n","ev","str","^Tempy","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"speaker_name","re":true},"ev","str","^left","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"active_sprite","re":true},"ev","str","^Surprised","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"left_sprite","re":true},"^Ohh, and then they'll be easier to land on even if they're faster? That might work!","\n","ev","str","^Happy","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"left_sprite","re":true},"^Worth a try at least!","\n","ev","str","^Gus","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"speaker_name","re":true},"ev","str","^right","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"active_sprite","re":true},"ev","str","^Happy","/str","/ev",{"VAR=":"right_sprite","re":true},"^Alright, moving platforms, take two!","\n",["done",{"#f":5,"#n":"g-0"}],null],"done",{"global decl":["ev","str","^default","/str",{"VAR=":"speaker_name"},"str","^Sad","/str",{"VAR=":"left_sprite"},"str","^Default","/str",{"VAR=":"right_sprite"},"str","^left","/str",{"VAR=":"active_sprite"},"str","^V2","/str",{"VAR=":"sprite_quality"},"/ev","end",null],"#f"